Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:04.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野多年后的突然出现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:08.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是为了告诉我 木户卷入了糟糕的事件中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.89,0:00:13.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,事件幕后 有曾经和木户一起建立公司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:18.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,M.A.R.S会社的共同代表 野野村 和人工智能程序GUMP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:22.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,然后 事件的中心 是那本游戏攻略
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.57,0:00:27.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切 都是从我们的机厅开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:36.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野么 帮我和木户说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:42.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要笔记本的话 就来渡边机厅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:46.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,和我用太空战机来决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:49.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,如果你赢了的话 就把笔记本给你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:52.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,如果 逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:55.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,或者我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:01.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我就把笔记本给那些家伙 让他们帮我还清债务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:12.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:15.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,能借我点钱不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:17.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:22.22,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,真的么 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:24.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:28.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.10,0:01:31.95,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:40.11,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 做慰问金的话也太多了吧 KID
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.40,0:01:43.01,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治说 机厅快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:44.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:46.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:48.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这么多钱怎么来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:51.47,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:55.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,为了开发最初的系统准备出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:57.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,KID
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:01:59.79,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:01.71,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是约定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:04.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,为了保住叔叔的机厅 做什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个机厅已经不再是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.13,0:02:08.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是礼治的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:11.23,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,即使垮掉了 也无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:14.43,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但是礼治不希望看到那样 所以才来找我借钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:17.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,而且我这边 再存钱就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:23.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,KID 你是One Coin就达到Counter Stop的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:03:00.00,注释,,0000,0000,0000,Banner;15;0;80,Counter Stop:指的是游戏中得分达到一定程度后无法再得分的情况，比如某游戏的等级最高是99，得分是999999分时就到达顶点，不能再升级得分了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,游戏就已经很难了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:27.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,人生想达到顶端就更难了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:29.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,即使失败 也是理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:30.21,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:33.17,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,所以 只有这次 我替礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:34.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,只有这次的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:36.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,就还会有“只有” 再有“只有”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:38.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,然后 就戒不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:41.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不久 金尽缘散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:42.86,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不是都这么说么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:44.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.65,0:02:48.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是必须由礼治自己跨越的困难
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:50.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:54.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,如果是他的话 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:57.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是他自己决定的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:02:59.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,即使失败
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:03.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,在下一场游戏也可能取得High Score
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.27,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,KID
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,就用这些钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:15.16,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,去玩你自己的“游戏”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:18.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我的“游戏”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:23.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:25.63,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个 能帮我保管一下么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:34.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:37.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是你重要的攻略笔记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:41.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是的 正因为如此才希望由叔叔来保管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:44.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,里面关于游戏的各种思考
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:46.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,都是我在那个机厅里玩游戏时想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.20,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那它对你今后的发展不是很重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:51.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,当需要的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:54.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我会去渡边机厅的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:57.21,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:03:59.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直等你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:01.21,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,KID
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:10.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:12.01,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你食言了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:14.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:18.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治的传话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:20.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要笔记本的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:23.55,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,在渡边机厅 用太空战机来决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:25.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:30.68,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 太空战机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:34.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:38.22,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我送你去吧 KID
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:56.37,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊 木户
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:03.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,完全成为红人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:05.56,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:08.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,让别人的店倒闭 自己却是钱人过的很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:09.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,误会 -我不想听那些狡辩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:14.56,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:17.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,快点开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:21.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们之间的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:23.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂正正地决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.35,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:28.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:31.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你来做裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:48.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,从1P的礼治开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:49.95,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:32.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治 那个攻略
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:40.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们两个人做的攻略
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:44.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 后面全是你自己找出来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:46.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的Game史
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:49.68,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,果然 是那个么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:54.01,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治 你又说不会再玩游戏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:56.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这么好玩的游戏怎么可能不玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:16.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是从那个时候开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:21.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,从那开始 游戏对我来说不再只是玩乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:26.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,最开始 是因为独自就可以开心 而喜欢上游戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:31.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在这个机厅遇见了礼治和高野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:37.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,发现了通过游戏 和他人在一起也可以很快乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:56.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我让机厅倒闭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:04.64,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你就像是这家机厅的继承之星一样 被生下来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:05.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快点看店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:09.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,谁稀罕继承这间破店 不过是一间游戏店而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,直到遇见你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.56,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,头一次感觉作为游戏厅老板的儿子是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,所以 想要守护这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:23.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,老爸说 把这里给卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:25.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,店关门了 卖给别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:28.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里对于我们来说 是非常重要的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不接受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:32.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我来当这里的老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,有干一辈子的自信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:41.64,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,当然不会麻烦老妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:46.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但还是没办到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:54.67,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,需要钱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我来做游戏赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:59.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,所以把机厅借的钱全部还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:00.84,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,别碰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:04.99,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要接受你的救济啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:35.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:41.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:42.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:48.99,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,还有2P呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:11.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:14.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但是即使是这样 希望你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:16.27,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我事实上曾找过你父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,行了 别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:19.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:26.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个混蛋老爸 装模做样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:29.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他儿子有多痛苦煎熬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:32.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.11,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:19.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户 这个还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:22.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,反正我拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:25.37,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,也只能拿来当柴烧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:29.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 虽然我确实很缺钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:31.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:37.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,游戏时间到此结束 木户
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:39.91,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,野野村
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:43.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:47.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,游戏结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:52.43,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,把你交给警察 GUMP就是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:55.79,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:59.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们一起想出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:03.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,游戏不是把它想出来的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:06.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,游戏一旦做成后就是玩家的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:10.51,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你的口头禅吗 木户
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:15.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后GUMP是我们的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,野野村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:18.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:22.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,把笔记给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:28.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:30.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,喂 木户 你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:31.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但是 野野村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:34.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,给你可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:36.75,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们有我们的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:38.47,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我们的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.56,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:45.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,把笔记给你 作为交换
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:49.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,把这个游戏厅的赎金给我们 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,喂 木户 -KID
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你既然知道这本笔记的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.35,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那你应该知道这不算贵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:55.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:58.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:03.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,M.A.R.S.社已经不是我的容身之地了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:07.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我辞职 把公司的股份全部转让给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:10.11,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,然后 再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:13.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,经营我们的游戏厅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:18.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,游戏厅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:21.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,在这个智能手机游戏的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:22.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此才要经营机厅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:26.91,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请遵守约定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:30.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,如果不马上转账的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:34.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我就把笔记烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:37.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 GUMP也就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:06.94,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,算你老实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:22.27,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:27.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我和你的游戏也从此GAME OVER了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:29.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:31.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:34.99,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不是木户
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:37.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,NOCON • KID （一币通关小子）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:56.24,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,已经是早上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:10.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:16.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,GUMP对我来说已经没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:21.47,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:25.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:27.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,并且
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:29.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户你不后悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:35.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,教会我的正是高野啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:36.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:39.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,并非知道了个人情报就能成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:43.01,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是因为在这个游戏厅里遇见了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:44.75,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我们才成为了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:49.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不管相隔多远
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:52.21,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,尽管 大家都过着自己的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:53.94,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,只要来这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:55.94,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要继续经营这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:16:00.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这次 我要玩“我们的游戏”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:03.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:09.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我们再开一次游戏厅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:16.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,看来我确实是这个游戏厅的继承之星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:20.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 大叔也经常这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:21.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:25.22,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我们的游戏厅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:30.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,很期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:36.91,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.57,0:16:40.43,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我们的游戏厅随时恭候您的光临哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治 KID
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:44.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那么 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:56.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治 就像大叔说的那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:58.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:02.68,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,他说她会成为很有魅力的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:06.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,确实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:09.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,离开的身影也毫无破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:14.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好了 债务也没了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,翻开崭新的一页 加油干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:19.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:22.19,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,虽然因为我的笔记赎回了机厅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:24.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但债你还是得还的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:29.23,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:31.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,“继往”开来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:36.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好好在机厅工作来还债吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:42.16,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,只好硬着头皮干了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:47.86,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次的游戏厅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:50.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,要做成集合我们曾经热爱的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:52.37,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,和将来的游戏的 梦想游戏厅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:55.71,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,一币通关 继往开来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:58.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,未来 游戏千变万化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:01.63,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们始终不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:05.95,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,始终不变地天天打游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:08.22,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 KID
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:13.95,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:14.83,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:17.68,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,天安门开咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:36.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 封顶了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:43.55,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个 怎么样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:53.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我终于把GUMP弄到手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:01.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:07.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:14.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:18.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:29.95,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:21.55,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,危险危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:23.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 兑换这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:25.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:27.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,200万日元 兑换
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:28.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,200万日元
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:29.22,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:33.23,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,很热闹啊 给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:36.14,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 100万日元
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:37.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不够哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:58.11,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户老师 让我看看怎么封顶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:20:59.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我 我也想看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.46,0:21:01.14,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,封底不是那么简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:03.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到  -第一次看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:04.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,真的好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:05.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:06.64,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法啦 让你们看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:11.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:50.94,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野文美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.41,0:22:59.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.71,0:23:10.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.65,0:23:11.81,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 我会一直支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:13.21,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.11,0:23:15.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:21.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,一枚硬币就能通关的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:23.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,被我们称为为通关小子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:26.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.17,0:23:28.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,一币通关小子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.14,0:23:30.35,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是他的绰号
